thread.title: Natalia Albina
thread.title_full: Temple & Webster reviewed by Natalia Albina

author: Natalia Albina
title: Natalia Albina
text: I ordered a cat scratching pole. Temple and Webster had the best selection of this item on their website. The one I ordered was not cheap, but it looks like a piece of furniture, and definitely doesn't spoil the look of my living room. Ordering process was very easy to follow. Delivery took very little time.
